488
00:33:57,565 --> 00:34:00,359
l'm here to say
that l would like...

489
00:34:00,443 --> 00:34:02,361
to start over.

490
00:34:03,988 --> 00:34:05,448
Friends.

491
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:09,952
Fuck you, man.
You're a liar.

492
00:34:09,994 --> 00:34:11,996
