692
00:48:56,631 --> 00:48:59,091
That's another one for David Kahane.(

693
00:49:02,720 --> 00:49:06,599
David was working on something the day
he died. l'd like to share it with you.

694
00:49:07,975 --> 00:49:10,978
'Blackness.
